<p>title: Endnotes
latexconfig: article</p>

<h1>Reference Style</h1>

<p>foo [^note].</p>

<p>[^note]: This is a footnote.</p>

<p>foo [#cite].</p>

<p>[#cite]: This is a citation.</p>

<p>foo [?<em>glossary</em>].</p>

<p>[?<em>glossary</em>]: This is a glossary term.</p>

<h1>Inline Style</h1>

<p>foo [^This is <em>another</em> footnote.].</p>

<p>foo [#This is <em>another</em> citation.].</p>

<p>foo [?(<em>gls</em>) This is <em>another</em> glossary term.]</p>

<h1>Extended Reference Style</h1>

<p>foo [^note3].</p>

<p>[^note3]: This is a footnote.</p>

<pre><code>&gt; With a *tail* block.
</code></pre>

<p>foo [#cite3].</p>

<p>[#cite3]: This is a citation.</p>

<pre><code>&gt; With a *tail* block.
</code></pre>

<p>foo [?glossary3].</p>

<p>[?glossary3]: This is a glossary term.</p>

<pre><code>&gt; With a *tail* block.
</code></pre>
